                                Need For Speed Undercover


                                                              
The cops are back like never before in this action-packed game of pursuit and betrayal! 

Go up against ruthless street racers out to win at any cost. Earn respect and fill your garage with the world's fastest cars. Reach the finish line first in circuit races. Bust up the city in bounty challenges. Show your skills for a shot at
top drivers.


Choose between Career or Quick Race mode. You're the hunter and the hunted in Need for Speed: Undercover.

This is the version with accelerometer support for devices with g-sensors like the Diamond/Pro
